A: At Int <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> up to</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 200 for each Int point you can just stick a decimal point in between your level and times by two. For example, at level 44 you would do this 44 = &gt; (4.4 * 2) = 8.8. For level 50 =&gt; (5.0 * 2) = 10. And so on up to a max of 12 points of mana @ level 60.<br>
<br>
